#: data/helpdata.txt:1607
msgid ""
"To add an item to the worklist, click the plus ( + ) icon on the Production "
"tab in the city dialog. A list of available items will appear. You can hover "
"over them for some brief help and then click the desired item to add to the "
"worklist of projects to build."
