#: data/helpdata.txt:1611
msgid ""
"You can remove an item from the worklist by double-clicking on it. Use the "
"buttons below the worklist to move items up and/or down in the list."
msgstr ""

#: data/helpdata.txt:1614
msgid ""
"If you want to buy the project that is first on the list, you can do that "
"from the top of the the Production tab in the city dialog."
msgstr ""

